  <entry>
    <title>如何將Json存入資料庫當中</title>
    <link href="https://robinsonweng.github.io/2019/09/19/json-to-database/"/>
    <id>https://robinsonweng.github.io/2019/09/19/json-to-database/</id>
    <published>2019-09-19T09:06:30.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-09-19T10:20:30.930Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="有兩種解決的方法"><a href="#有兩種解決的方法" class="headerlink" title="有兩種解決的方法"></a>有兩種解決的方法</h2><ol><li>在資料庫支援的情況下, 以Documention為輔完成任務</li><li>沒有資料庫不支援的情況下, 將Json的每個key拆開變成獨立的表格, 並加上ID建立所謂的關係來連結不同的表格</li></ol><blockquote><p>Json example:</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"id"</span>: <span class="string">"1"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"name"</span>: <span class="string">"Jane"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"hobby"</span>:<span class="string">"Cooking"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"Age"</span>: <span class="string">"10"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"Pet"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">"name"</span> :<span class="string">"David"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">"species"</span>: <span class="string">"Dog"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">"age"</span>: <span class="string">"4"</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"id"</span>: <span class="string">"2"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"name"</span>: <span class="string">"Lucy"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"hobby"</span>:<span class="string">"Jogging"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"Age"</span>: <span class="string">"18"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"Pet"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">"name"</span>: <span class="string">"Kitto"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">"species"</span>: <span class="string">"Cat"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">"age"</span>: <span class="string">"4"</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>Table example:</p></blockquote><p><code>table: Name</code></p><table><thead><tr><th>ID</th><th>Name</th><th align="left">Hobby</th><th align="center">Age</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>Jane</td><td align="left">Cooking</td><td align="center">10</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>Lucy</td><td align="left">Jogging</td><td align="center">18</td></tr></tbody></table><p><code>table: Pet</code></p><table><thead><tr><th>ID</th><th>Name</th><th align="center">species</th><th>Age</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>David</td><td align="center">Dog</td><td>4</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>Kitto</td><td align="center">Cat</td><td>4</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
